{"tid":2002731,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點先可以重拾學習熱情?","createTime":"2020-05-05T10:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T16:07:12.000Z","uid":175540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"172655c4fbb5170061ee9d76479cc7ff595276bd","tid":2002731,"uid":175540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"記得自己小學個陣好鐘意數學，玩奧數可以玩一日<br />\n之後入到一間唔錯嘅中學，但開始變懶唔想諗野，經常抄功課<br />\n依家負碌入到大學，但對學習冇咩興趣<br />\n自認自己唔廢，稍微溫一溫成績都OK<br />\n一開始對大部份野都冇咩興趣，但如果我慢慢學，突然諗通某樣野就會有興趣學落去<br />\n但問題係好難令自己踏出第一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7e96071ed8269f936e7c96ca81e6309304d054","tid":2002731,"uid":54528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:01:26.000Z","msg":"唔識咪無熱情, 笑撚死"},{"pid":"19d64a3f0fd040074cdfdacb07b986a11b587d07","tid":2002731,"uid":175540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df7e96071ed8269f936e7c96ca81e6309304d054","tid":2002731,"uid":54528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:01:26.000Z","msg":"唔識咪無熱情, 笑撚死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:03:08.000Z","msg":"關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識同熱情係兩樣野 你識做果份工唔等於有熱情"},{"pid":"6a12e0b54e8f4f234d8d01a48933b4a0f3d68f19","tid":2002731,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:08:10.000Z","msg":"你上次有熱情已經要追溯返小學<br />\n難啲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b251db854ffe0c7554a76fc76bb4ee1abb1b6369","tid":2002731,"uid":176415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"以前同你一樣<br />\n好想學野, 但總係搵唔到一樣肯上心持續去學<br />\n我既建議係番多 D 唔同既實習<br />\n唔同既實習經驗可以盡早幫你認清自己既興趣,擅長同需要"},{"pid":"e7a040304a2c9652875419a44581e9f8c7bfcddb","tid":2002731,"uid":244357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:05:28.000Z","msg":"係fb/reddit